title: DisCatSharp
description:
A C# wrapper library for Discord's API. Enables developers to create Discord bots!

As a web developer I wanted to host, and integrate bots in a web host environment. I contributed to DisCatSharp by creating the Hosting and Configuration modules.

title: DisCatSharp Project Templates
description: This contains a few C# project templates tailored for the Hosting and Configuration modules. As a developer, or newcomer to the library getting started is as easy as project new!
